Package net.regsirius06.engine.core.graphics.labyrinth.default2D

package net.regsirius06.engine.core.graphics.labyrinth.default2D
Provides the classes and logic for rendering a 2D labyrinth environment with raycasting effects. This package includes classes responsible for visualizing the player's perspective of the labyrinth, including light sources, reflections, and walls.

The key class in this package is LabyrinthGraphics2D, which implements the ray casting logic to simulate how the player sees the world based on their position and orientation.

This package is part of the larger engine that simulates a 2D labyrinth world, and it is designed to be extendable for rendering different types of 2D environments with ray casting features.
